import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Socket } from 'ngx-socket-io'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { data: any; title = 'webangular'; constructor(private socket: Socket) { } ngOnInit() { this.data = [] this.socket.on('topico', (data: any) => { console.log(data); this.data.push(data); }); this.socket.emit('subscribe', { topic: 'topico' }) } }
